value.string: Navigation To Sch Person Property BOT
To Navigate till Scheduled Personal Property screen and call "Sch Person Property Flag Check BOT" to validate it contains Y or Not.
1. Navigating to scheduled personal property screen by click on Display->Endorsement->Address bar.
2. Call sub bot "Sch Person Property Flag Check BOT" to validate it contains Y or Not.
